sub_title: Technical Director at Jordan Football Association
summary:
Specialized in Elite Youth Football development within the age groups U6 till U21

International working experience since 2002 with the best youth academies and educators around the world; Netherlands, North Ireland, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, Mexico, Kazakhstan and United Arab emirates.

Quality before Quantity, Getting the max out of the player, team, coaches and infrastructure. Being Innovation, Creative, Organizer, Think in Process after Product, Give to the people!
